Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:19.14,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Mugyu-gyu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.79,0:00:35.85,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,I thought you'd both vanished again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:44.87,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,I read through Tsumugi-san's diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.09,0:00:48.18,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,I kinda figured things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.18,0:00:49.71,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,What Tsumugi's purpose is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:54.39,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,What this girl means when \Nshe says she's "going back."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.39,0:00:55.67,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.94,0:00:59.72,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Well, whatever the case, to us, \NTsumugi's just Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.10,0:01:03.72,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, \Nwe'll be with her to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:05.37,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,That's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:09.31,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:14.57,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Shizuku, I came up with a stupid idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:23.09,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Good morning, Hairi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:25.20,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Mugyu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:27.67,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,You're here too, Shizuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.39,0:01:31.47,Default,Hairi; Shizuku,0,0,0,,Morning, Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:37.86,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:12.02,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Happy New Year, Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:18.69,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Today's actually January 1st.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:20.24,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Mugyu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:22.65,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I had this idea just earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:26.24,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,What if we squeeze a whole\Nyear's worth of big events,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:28.42,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,New Year's, cherry blossoms, and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:32.10,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,into the week we have before August 31st?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:33.42,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,A whole year's worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:36.96,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,No, make it a lifetime's worth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:39.23,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,That's fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:42.51,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,We can do Halloween and Christmas \Nand everything all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:44.71,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,That's too silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:48.74,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Each event has its own customs specifically\N for the season and that time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:52.24,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Well, it can be disrespectful \Nto do things too late,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:54.61,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,but there's no harm doing things early.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:59.52,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I don't know, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:00.53,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:05.86,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'm not suggesting this just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:06.96,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Mugyu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:08.09,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:12.58,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,I want to get in as much fun as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:14.86,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Decades' worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:15.87,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Shizuku...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.39,0:04:17.75,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:20.62,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:25.62,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:33.22,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I want to play lots and lots\N with you and Shizuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:35.02,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:42.12,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I want to be with you forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:45.28,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fax.2\fnArial Black\c&H8C7AF1&\3c&HFFFEFF&\pos(372.338,117.962)\frz347}Shaved Ice
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:47.28,Default,Ao,0,0,0,,A lifetime's worth of events?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:48.92,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,You're asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:50.16,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Why should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:51.29,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(440,1)\an5\fnImpact\shad0\fax-.2\c&H6ED475&\fs10\3c&HF4FDFB&\pos(486.684,52.607)\frz17.73}Watermelon Bar
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:53.08,Default,Ryoichi,0,0,0,,You can count on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:54.71,Default,Tenzen,0,0,0,,W-We'd be happy to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:58.00,Default,Miki,0,0,0,,In that case, I'd be delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:04:59.24,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:01.13,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,We owe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:04.34,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,This should be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:05.34,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:09.24,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Oh, and for the last day, August 31st,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.76,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'm thinking we should have a birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:13.14,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,That sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:14.89,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Let's make it a big celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:18.60,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I was thinking... maybe we\N can have a surprise of some sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:21.12,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,A surprise, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:24.44,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,This time, {\i1}I{\i0} have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:32.33,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,And so, that was how the\N final week of our summer began.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:25.13,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,We made it such a busy summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:28.13,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,It almost felt wrong\Nto waste any time breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:30.63,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnArial\fs18\shad0\c&H442B13&\3c&HC48F54&}Takahara Hairi\N{\fs16}-Tsumugi Wenders
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.54,0:06:35.64,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,We made sure that summer break\N was the best we'd ever remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:41.15,Default,All,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:43.96,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:47.65,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I have a Christmas present \Nfor the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:50.90,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Spare keys to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:58.62,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Now you two can come in if you ever\N want to hang out when I'm not home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:00.23,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:03.73,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You're pretty forward though, Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:05.92,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Giving your boyfriend a spare key and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.02,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Mugyu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:10.59,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I-I didn't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.98,0:07:12.72,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I did mean it like that, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:15.97,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,I have a gift for you too, Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:17.31,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:21.10,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:27.94,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,It's a swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:30.38,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:31.70,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,L-Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:34.37,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,I thought her boobies might react somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:38.19,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,now that she's in a relationship \Nwith you, Pairi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:45.69,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,There's no way they're getting \Nbigger than yours, Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:49.79,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:52.15,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,That much, I'm sure of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:56.18,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:59.45,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,I meant it in the hopes \Nthat they'll grow bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:14.45,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Tsumugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:18.49,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I don't wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:20.89,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I don't want to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:22.22,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:26.19,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I still want to go to the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:28.93,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I want to wear a yukata to a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:31.33,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I want to have a snow fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:34.62,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,There's so much I still want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:42.31,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I want to be with you two forever and forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:48.10,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,It's okay, Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:50.32,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:53.07,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:56.57,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,When tomorrow comes, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:59.88,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,We're going to have fun together \Nuntil the end, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:02.70,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,So we have to stay smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:04.67,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Right, Pairi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:05.25,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.66,0:09:06.65,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:07.58,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:11.73,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,We're going to be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:15.42,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Hairi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:18.73,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,So no more crying, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:21.10,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Why, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:25.64,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Why are you both so nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:27.87,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Why else?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:30.98,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Because I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:32.02,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:33.48,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:37.32,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,M-Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:42.98,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Shizuka, Hairi-san... I love you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:48.11,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,And so we came to August 31st,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:51.28,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,the last day of summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:01.39,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:03.53,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,I have lots to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:05.81,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Spend some quality time with Pairi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:07.72,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Mugyu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:10.52,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I want to spend more time with you, Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:12.47,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Don't be so down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:14.40,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,We had plenty of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:17.46,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,I had a really great time, Hairi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:18.90,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Shizuku...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:19.70,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:22.87,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,I love you, Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.27,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I love you too, Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:28.00,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,No tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:29.12,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:32.75,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.31,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Tsumugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:54.02,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Tsumugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.32,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Hairi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:01.03,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:05.82,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Tsumugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:08.59,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Could you tell me you love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:09.54,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Mugyu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:12.54,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I want to remember your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:16.42,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I want to remember yours too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.18,0:11:20.30,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I love you, Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:23.18,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I love you, Hairi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:42.10,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Looks like it's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:44.36,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Is something about to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:45.86,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.86,0:11:46.87,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:48.57,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Mugyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:51.12,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,You're being mean, Hairi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:19.33,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,This is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:21.47,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Today is your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:24.25,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,So we have to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:28.28,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,With a lifetime's worth \Nof birthday cake candles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:31.33,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,It's my birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:35.79,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,But how did you even find all these candles?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:37.72,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,The youth group people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:39.17,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,They helped?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:43.67,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,They were all on board with \NShizuku's idea to make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:47.01,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,They made these using empty Paringles cans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:51.72,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Paringles really are the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:19.60,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,They're all such good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:20.32,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:22.86,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You couldn't ask for better friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:30.58,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Hairi-san, may I talk about the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:31.22,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.72,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Tsumugi-chan is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:36.85,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,That song I've been humming
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:42.86,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,is one she used to sing when \Nshe was at her house beyond the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:48.86,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,She didn't have many friends here,\N so she never sang it much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:52.87,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Her only friends were her stuffed animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:58.08,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,But one day, she befriended \Na girl named Katou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.08,0:14:00.38,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,She was so happy telling me about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:06.38,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Then she fell in love, and she decided \Nto leave the island with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:07.92,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:13.06,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Tsumugi-chan vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:19.73,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fs16\shad0\bord3\fnArial\an7\c&H533724&\3c&HECD698&\b1}Father, Mother, I'm sorry.\NAnd to everyone on the island, thank you.\NI love you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:23.73,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Still, I'm sure she'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:30.07,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,So I decided to take her place until then,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:34.16,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,in hopes that no one would forget her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:44.21,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I tried searching for Tsumugi-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:47.21,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,asking if anyone knew me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:54.71,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,But fewer and fewer people \Nwere left who remembered her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:59.60,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Then one day, Katou-san came.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:04.59,Flashback,Katou,0,0,0,,Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:11.83,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,She told me to do\N what I wanted from then on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:13.92,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,What you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:20.28,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,The thing is, I didn't know\N what I wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:30.34,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Which is why I decided to make friends \Nfor when Tsumugi-chan found her way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:33.64,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Before I left this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:36.55,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,And one day, I met someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:40.20,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,She complimented the stuffed animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:43.31,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,That simple occasion led me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:47.20,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,to have a new friend named Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:51.78,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Then I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:53.86,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I fell in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.86,0:15:56.02,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Not for Tsumugi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:16:00.04,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I fell in love for my own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:03.23,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I've made lots of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:06.07,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I've come to know happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:10.05,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Now there's so much I want to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:15.87,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I can't wait to see what happens next.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:19.80,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,It'll probably snow when winter arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:21.81,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,And it'll be a real ordeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:24.77,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,The snow will jam the door shut,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:28.79,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,and I'll miraculously make it out\Nthanks to you and Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:30.90,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,You'll save my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:32.49,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:35.36,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,In the summer, we'll swim at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:38.00,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,We'll wear yukatas and go to a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:40.80,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Sometimes we'll get in fights,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:43.54,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,but we'll make up right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.54,0:16:48.04,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,And I'll tell you how glad I am\Nthat the three of us are together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:48.75,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:50.83,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:51.95,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:54.73,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Today was fun too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:55.82,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:17:01.58,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,And tomorrow and the next day \Nand every day after will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:02.87,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:08.65,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I have Shizuku and Shiroha-san too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:13.62,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Then there's Ao-san and Nomura-san \Nand Mitani-san and Kanou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:16.03,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Every day's gonna be so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:19.28,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:23.48,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Please don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:25.09,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:26.43,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:28.79,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You won't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:39.24,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Hairi-san, I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:40.93,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I got to meet everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:42.85,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I got to meet Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:45.55,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I got to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.03,0:17:47.72,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:50.86,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'm happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:54.36,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,So we have to have fun, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:17:58.18,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:08.32,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,It was such a beautiful summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:16.88,Lyrics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I sing in search of me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:23.01,Lyrics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Mu-mugyugyugyugyu, mu-mugyugyugyugyu, \Nmugyugyumugyugyugyu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:29.73,Lyrics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I sing at the lighthouse \Nso that I can be found
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:35.87,Lyrics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Mu-mugyugyugyugyu, mu-mugyugyugyugyu, \Nmugyugyumugyugyugyu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:42.54,Lyrics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Looking for materials, the strong bird does
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,0:18:48.71,Lyrics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Mu-mugyugyugyugyu, mu-mugyugyugyugyu, \Nmugyugyumugyugyugyu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:55.13,Lyrics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,The bird, the cow, and I play in the water
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:19:01.47,Lyrics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Mu-mugyugyugyugyu, mu-mugyugyugyugyu, \Nmugyugyumugyugyugyu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:07.97,Lyrics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,The bird and the cow and I\N are together this summer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:14.36,Lyrics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Mu-mugyugyugyugyu, mu-mugyugyugyugyu, \Nmugyugyumugyugyugyu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:20.98,Lyrics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,The bird and I hold hands; we are lovers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:27.12,Lyrics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Mu-mugyugyugyugyu, mu-mugyugyugyugyu, \Nmugyugyumugyugyugyu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:40.05,Lyrics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,My beloved bird, my beloved cow
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:46.22,Lyrics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Mu-mugyugyugyugyu, mu-mugyugyugyugyu, \Nmugyugyumugyugyugyu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.22,0:19:52.85,Lyrics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,The sky-blue ribbon is my treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:58.86,Lyrics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Mu-mugyugyugyugyu, mu-mugyugyugyugyu, \Nmugyugyumugyugyugyu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:05.70,Lyrics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,I won't forget this summer, \Nthis lighthouse, this island
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:12.32,Lyrics,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Mu-mugyugyugyugyu, mu-mugyugyugyugyu, \Nmugyugyumugyugyugyu
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:44.78,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:55.01,Default,Hairi; Shizuku,0,0,0,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:05.93,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,It's been a good summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:11.20,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:15.48,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Tsumugi was summer break itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:16.69,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:20.19,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,You meet someone for the first \Ntime somewhere unfamiliar
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:21.63,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,and become friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:25.42,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,It feels like you have all \Nthe time in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:29.17,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,But in the end, you grieve \Nwhen your time is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.17,0:21:31.70,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,You regret having to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:34.74,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,She was my summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:35.52,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:37.44,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Mine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:39.27,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.47,0:21:44.71,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,That song!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.39,0:21:47.00,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,What are you singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:52.58,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,The cat lady who does the radio \Ncalisthenics sometimes was singing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:55.05,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,We made friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:55.98,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:21:58.60,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Then hopefully you'll see her next year too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:21:59.31,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:01.88,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Next year, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.81,0:22:05.21,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.75,0:22:07.36,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:08.24,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:12.01,Default,Shizuku,0,0,0,,Summer break will come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.41,0:22:26.88,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Cotton Candy-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:30.60,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,See you again, Tsumugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:22:57.76,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.22,0:22:59.80,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,See you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.74,0:23:29.94,Default,Hairi; Shizuku,0,0,0,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.09,0:23:34.57,Default,Tsumugi,0,0,0,,Welcome back!

